title: Money Tree

title: Cat Palm
description: Cat Palm comes planted in a 10-inch modern decor pot—a very contemporary look! This healthy plant ships at a minimum of 34 inches tall, measuring from the bottom of the pot. Ships fast, direct from our farm to your home!

title: Peace Lily
description: Bring home a beautiful Peace Lily to add a relaxing, calm feel to any space. These houseplants are natural air purifiers that help keep your indoor air fresh and clean. Easily fits tabletop, shelf, living room, office, or bedroom decor

title: Alocasia Elephant Ear California
description: Alocasia Gageana California, also known as Alocasia Elephant Ear, is a beautiful house plant with distinctive leaves. The plant’s medium green leaves are glossy and stiff, with strong bony veins that give the edges a scalloped effect

title: Alocasia Polly African Mask
description: Alocasia Polly is a beautiful house plant with distinctive leaves. The arrowhead- or shield-shaped leaves have large, protruding white veins running through them, which contrast strongly with the rest of the dark green leaf

title: Fiddle Leaf Fig
description: The Fiddle Leaf Fig is also called ficus lyrata and is a popular indoor evergreen plant with large green 'fiddle' or violin shaped leaves
